# packages/dependency/internal/adapters/spwn/content/ is the
# go:generate mirror of /catalog/ — committed intentionally so
# `go build` / `go:embed` work on a fresh checkout without first
# running `go generate`. `make test` (and the go-generate step it
# runs) refreshes it to match /catalog/; any diff should land in the
# same commit as the catalog change. Not listed here on purpose.
